<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>菩萨 - 标签 - 无名老人</title><link>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/tags/%E8%8F%A9%E8%90%A8/</link><description>无名老人的文章</description><generator>Hugo 0.160.1 &amp; FixIt v0.4.5</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Wed, 01 Apr 2026 19:00:00 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/tags/%E8%8F%A9%E8%90%A8/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>偈子：法住经</title><link>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/%E6%B3%95%E4%BD%8F%E7%BB%8F/</link><pubDate>Wed, 01 Apr 2026 19:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/%E6%B3%95%E4%BD%8F%E7%BB%8F/</guid><description>&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h1 class="heading-element" id="法住经"&gt;&lt;span&gt;法住经&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e6%b3%95%e4%bd%8f%e7%bb%8f" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;关键词&lt;/strong&gt;：法住经、末法、正法、佛告阿难、比丘、护持、菩萨、修行、佛法、护法&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 class="heading-element" id="前言"&gt;&lt;span&gt;前言&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e5%89%8d%e8%a8%80" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;　　《法住经》乃佛陀为阿难开示末法时期正法住世因缘之经典。经文直指佛灭度后，弟子们或舍正法、贪利养、习戏论，或持戒者遭毁辱，以致天龙远离、大臣不敬，正法渐灭；然亦有少欲知足、护持禁戒之比丘，及爱惜正法之长者居士、善男信女，乃至菩萨乘本愿力而生于此时，护持如来无上正法，作大饶益。今录此经文，愿诸佛子共参共勉。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>四圣谛</title><link>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/%E5%9B%9B%E5%9C%A3%E8%B0%9B%E7%9C%9F%E5%AE%9E%E4%B9%89/</link><pubDate>Wed, 01 Apr 2026 18:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/%E5%9B%9B%E5%9C%A3%E8%B0%9B%E7%9C%9F%E5%AE%9E%E4%B9%89/</guid><description>&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h1 class="heading-element" id="四圣谛真实义"&gt;&lt;span&gt;四圣谛真实义&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e5%9b%9b%e5%9c%a3%e8%b0%9b%e7%9c%9f%e5%ae%9e%e4%b9%89" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;关键词&lt;/strong&gt;：四圣谛、苦集灭道、大般涅槃经、声闻缘觉、菩萨、外道、有漏无漏、解脱、佛子、无取无舍&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 class="heading-element" id="前言"&gt;&lt;span&gt;前言&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e5%89%8d%e8%a8%80" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;　　佛对五比丘说：你们五位，苦应知，集应断，灭应证，道应修，苦集灭道是真实不虚的，你们若不解苦集灭道四圣谛的真实甚深义，那么与解脱是无缘的。四圣谛乃学佛人入佛门的共法，也是解脱的基础大法。不解此义者，皆是佛在《大般涅槃经》中所说“&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;一切众生皆依非真邪伪之法&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;”的盲修瞎练者，何以故？著相著魔故。今依经义，详述四圣谛之真实甚深义。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>大乘义</title><link>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/%E4%BD%9B%E5%AD%90%E5%BA%94%E6%82%9F%E5%A4%A7%E4%B9%98%E4%B9%89/</link><pubDate>Wed, 01 Apr 2026 15:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/%E4%BD%9B%E5%AD%90%E5%BA%94%E6%82%9F%E5%A4%A7%E4%B9%98%E4%B9%89/</guid><description>&lt;h1 class="heading-element" id="佛子应悟大乘义方离自误愚"&gt;&lt;span&gt;佛子应悟大乘义，方离自误愚&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e4%bd%9b%e5%ad%90%e5%ba%94%e6%82%9f%e5%a4%a7%e4%b9%98%e4%b9%89%e6%96%b9%e7%a6%bb%e8%87%aa%e8%af%af%e6%84%9a" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;关键词&lt;/strong&gt;：大般涅槃经、无所得、菩萨、大乘、六祖、自性、净戒、佛性、心行、觉悟&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 class="heading-element" id="前言"&gt;&lt;span&gt;前言&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e5%89%8d%e8%a8%80" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;本文汇集《大般涅槃经》《宝积经》《法华经》《四十二章经》及六祖慧能大师开示，阐明菩萨净戒、无所得义、自性自度之真谛，以警末世学佛人依佛知见，离颠倒执，入正定聚。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>大乘义</title><link>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/bodhisattva-meaning/</link><pubDate>Sun, 29 Oct 2017 23:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/bodhisattva-meaning/</guid><description>&lt;h1 class="heading-element" id="佛子应悟大乘义方离自误愚"&gt;&lt;span&gt;佛子应悟大乘义，方离自误愚&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e4%bd%9b%e5%ad%90%e5%ba%94%e6%82%9f%e5%a4%a7%e4%b9%98%e4%b9%89%e6%96%b9%e7%a6%bb%e8%87%aa%e8%af%af%e6%84%9a" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;关键词&lt;/strong&gt;：大般涅槃经、大乘、无所得、自性、菩萨、善爱、净戒、六祖、法华经、如来&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 class="heading-element" id="前言"&gt;&lt;span&gt;前言&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e5%89%8d%e8%a8%80" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;末世学佛，多迷四大为身，妄想为心，心外求法，愈求愈苦。佛于《大般涅槃经》中分明开示善爱、不善爱之别，菩萨无所得之真实义，以及清净持戒之五法佐助。又引《宝积经》、《法华经》及六祖法语，直指自性自度、心行佛道。今依经教，一字不易，略加分节，以助佛子悟入大乘，远离自误。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>